  carbohydrates: 85 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 44 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 860 mg
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/teriyaki-chicken-tenders-5a664231ad1d6c6f007d0d72
time required: 35 minutes
author: Michelle Doll Olson
cuisine: Asian
